creator: Fachschaftsrat Informatik
descriptionHtml:
This app gives you the possibility to access to the most important services in your student life at the Fachhochschule Dortmund easily and on the go.

Timetable
-Official timetables of the FB4 (if desired, filtered by groupletter)
-Add or edit official (and custom) events
-Share your timetable via NFC

News
-New messages of the faculties IT and economy
-Search for specific messages
-Share messages

Menu
-Menus and opening times of all restaurants of the Studentenwerk Dortmund
-Sort menus or hide them if not relevant

Links/Downloads
-Links to pages like Ilias, ODS and SmartAssign
-Download of audit plan, semester schedule and locationplan

NRWTicket
-Download your ticket directly from the ODS
-Display it in the app
descriptionShort: Timetable-App for the FB4 of the Fachhochschule Dortmund.
